I remember back in 2005 when I was playing the game I didn't even knew what I was doing I was only shooting to the characters I didn't even knew if they were my teammates or not. I was having fun with this game. And I still do, I was 6yo at the time now I'm 18yo and I think I'm having more fun than I used to have.

Pros: 
- Fits for almost every computer;
- Excluding the little violence its good for almost all ages;
- You can increase your fps skills a lot;
- You can play with friends, like 20 people;
- So many diferent and original gamemodes;
- More than 100 Maps;
- Cheap for the game itself;
- Its very funny.

Cons:
- Classic game, classic bugs;
- For 2004 it actually has good graphics but we are in 2017;
- Getting really low on players;

You should play the game once or twice, give it a try and tell me what you thought of it.

WARNING: If you play the game add me to play with you :)
